original_title: Mozart Violin Concertos 1-5 & Sinfonia Concertante in E Flat
overview: Gidon Kremer performs the complete Mozart Violin Concertos plus the Sinfonia concertante with violist Kim Kashkashian. Nikolaus Harnoncourt conducts the VIenna Philharmonic. The works were filmed in Vienna between 1983 and 1987.
title: Mozart Violin Concertos 1-5 & Sinfonia Concertante in E Flat
